	; ── MSPM0 power switch (DMG2305UX P-MOSFET, default ON) ───────────────────
	; GPIO17 HIGH = Q_PWR gate pulled high via R_GATE → MOSFET OFF → MSPM0 power off
	; R_PD holds gate LOW when Pi GPIO is tristated → MSPM0 default ON
